body:
Wow, it may not seem a lot compared to other youtubers but boy am I pleased to hit 200 subscribers. I could not of done it without any of you guys and thanks for all your support. You guys seriously are the best and words cannot describe how happy I am :). I will be releasing a 200 Subscriber Montage very shortly after writing this post to thank you guys for my achievement :D.

Thank you very much and have a nice day <3

EDIT: Oh my god. Wow. 200 Subscribers although it may not seem a lot I am so happy that I hit this achievement. And with the start of 2016 and everything this is a great start to the year by me acomplishing this. I cannot thank you guys enough and I love each and every one of you who subscribed and took the time to watch my videos thank you guys ever so much <3.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=If1YYdExafU&feature=youtu.be
